🐢 Turtle Strategy (ASML)


A classic trend-following system with dynamic position sizing


This is the primary strategy featuring:



Donchian channel breakout entry (15-day)


Donchian channel exit (12-day low)


Volatility-based stop loss (2.5× ATR)


Risk-proportional position sizing (1% per trade)



