📈 Original Breakout Strategy


A simplified ATR-based breakout with fixed exits


This baseline strategy features:



Donchian channel breakout entry (20-day)


Fixed percentage stop loss (-2.0%)


Fixed percentage profit target (+3.0%)


Fixed position size (100 shares)



